premise_source_doc_sentence: The Revolutionary Black Panther Party , claims continuity of the Black Panther Party of the 1960s , their leader Dr. Alli Muhammad MS , PhD , MD  (  title , Chief-General-In-Command / Commander  )  , was raised a Black Panther in the Black Panther Party of the 1960s-1980s which was dissolved in 1982 .

The Revolutionary Black Panther Party or RBPP  (  coined the continuity of the Black Panther Party , BPP  )  is a revolutionary black nationalist , Pan-African and socialist  (  Neo-Afrikan Socialist  )  group who is a defined as a `` Black military ''  (  militia  )  .

The Black Panther Party or the BPP  (  originally the Black Panther Party for Self-Defense  )  was a revolutionary black nationalist and socialist organization founded by Bobby Seale and Huey Newton in October 1966 .

The Ten-Point Program , or The Black Panther Party for Self-Defense Ten-Point Platform and Program , is a set of guidelines to the Black Panther Party and states their ideals and ways of operation , a `` combination of a Bill of Rights and a Declaration of Independence . ''
Mark 's wife was once blocked from entering a Black Panther Party  (  BPP  )  office by a Panther member .
